、蔣志光同惠英紅，甚至戲份唔多既番書仔阿海都搶過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n秀才愛上兵主線係大佬爺vs蘇鎮東蘇鎮南兄弟，佢同油米高條線wfc?v<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />v<br />\n帝女花?人地陳豪一句幫朕check下已經收佢皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n舊年套誘情轉駁，個個焦點都係法拉跳鋼管舞同uuu既煩膠配樂<br />\n佢同嘉欣BB合作N次，觀眾焦點都係擺係對手身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n皆大歡喜個個都鍾意洪白嵐<br />\n金石良緣既焦點都係嘉欣BB做mk妹同變賢妻<br />\n老友狗狗個個講吳尊多過佢扮圍村仔<br />\n蒲松齡個個唔係講嘉欣就係講法拉<br />\n當旺爸爸個撚個嘈押韻，雪雪雪都出位過佢<br />\n<br />\n但偏偏咁撚多戲拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗極都唔明<br />\n樣又唔係好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n觀眾緣又冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n戲又屎剩係識擺個屙屎唔出既正義樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又唔係好似bobby咁收視福將擔正既都好收視<br />\n又唔係好似林峰咁有家底<br />\n又唔係好似菊花泓咁賣屎忽俾大師做佢honey<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又唔係好似橡膠咁幫620奶西<br />\n但佢套撚套都做主角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又主持埋咩正識第一大廚出馬<br />\n懶係周身刀咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢仲要賤格到花名都冇一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你憎林峰可以叫佢淋瘋/ 亞太峰<br />\n你憎胡杏兒可以叫佢囧囧<br />\n你憎鄭嘉穎可以叫佢橡膠<br />\n你憎jeana可以叫佢賤娜<br />\n但憎佢呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只可以叫個九唔搭八既馬撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最核凸果點係你呢條柒姑碌成鳩日以為自己好有料係度懷才不遇咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要走就早走啦鬼撚留你條戇鳩仔咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又成日以為自己好撚好戲咁教人做戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屋企冇鏡都叫珍姐噴d西水俾你照下自己個死樣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後講多句<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">你條仆街馬撚咪以為依家扮晒正義撚就唔記得你當年搶撚左初哥哥既君好呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"2b22d58535076d936215a978f361d26cf89922cd","tid":2506043,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69f9bc7ac8f7838e68e4298a099e902f2b42451c","tid":2506043,"uid":54516,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6eec6b464c1fe6e98fb8a94e59da42c0f4d1f745","tid":2506043,"uid":283912,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"4ef252c7be06d83b8a4531156e2868c0fe0f5186","tid":2506043,"uid":134071,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T05:19:26.000Z","msg":"演技差，原來人品都差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T05:46:04.000Z","msg":"佢藍唔藍都係其次<br />\n本身樣又柒演技又差存在感又低<br />\n可以撈到今日做到男一都已經夠離奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T05:54:31.000Z","msg":"蜀中無大將，係CCTVB冇晒人才先上到位。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T05:57:22.000Z","msg":"仲要搵佢做藝訓班校長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cc4647b2fca4d0511b0342d307a8da12c59638a","tid":2506043,"uid":42246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T05:58:02.000Z","msg":"點解大家會期待契哥條撚樣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n條友讀北大好開心"},{"pid":"64100e8791a6a790dfaaaeaef73bdf9905bdada6","tid":2506043,"uid":54516,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2b22d58535076d936215a978f361d26cf89922cd","tid":2506043,"uid":134071,"lik