sets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你憎林峰可以叫佢淋瘋/ 亞太峰<br />\n你憎胡杏兒可以叫佢囧囧<br />\n你憎鄭嘉穎可以叫佢橡膠<br />\n你憎jeana可以叫佢賤娜<br />\n但憎佢呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只可以叫個九唔搭八既馬撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最核凸果點係你呢條柒姑碌成鳩日以為自己好有料係度懷才不遇咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要走就早走啦鬼撚留你條戇鳩仔咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又成日以為自己好撚好戲咁教人做戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屋企冇鏡都叫珍姐噴d西水俾你照下自己個死樣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後講多句<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">你條仆街馬撚咪以為依家扮晒正義撚就唔記得你當年搶撚左初哥哥既君好呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T06:12:55.000Z","msg":"屌你勁有潮文feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36b65552eb719fab49827e5e997824ae1853e58e","tid":2506043,"uid":218082,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b98b98e4d77ca9dd8952de2841680ce19d87d3d4","tid":2506043,"uid":54516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02a9e9b10a2b1b8ceda927ec7560f59278618cd3","tid":2506043,"uid":218082,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T05:49:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wWllep-QpnY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwWllep-QpnY&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oBAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=d6749f3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wWllep-QpnY</a><br />\n14:30<br />\n之前Barry Ma先話條馬撚搞舞台劇,請crew個陣話要政治中立唔請黃crew,最後台前幕後都藍撚到黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><